{"tid":1853355,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】高通 Qualcomm 捐款 700 萬元人民幣支持抗疫 跟隨 Starbucks．MediaTek 步伐？","createTime":"2020-01-31T02:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T05:18:22.000Z","uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e05f100b8a884ebe08e9fa206fc6fc6f1879e79","tid":1853355,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】高通 Qualcomm 捐款 700 萬元人民幣支持抗疫 跟隨 Starbucks．MediaTek 步伐？<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2550000/2551340/20200129_qualcomm_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2550000%2F2551340%2F20200129_qualcomm_02_600.jpg&h=a4290528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2550000/2551340/20200129_qualcomm_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2550000%2F2551340%2F20200129_qualcomm_04_600.jpg&h=4b14a0c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n隨着近日武漢肺炎疫情日益嚴重，不少名人及企業均表示會捐款捐口罩等物資，幫助中國全力抗疫。早前 Starbucks 中國在微博出 post 表示已捐款 300 萬元人民幣（約 HK$342 萬）予中國紅十字會，幫助採購口罩、防護衣等醫療物資，同時也在春節假期間關閉位於湖北省的 Starbucks 分店，以顧客健康安全為前提。而在科技界，高通 Qualcomm 也在微博出 post 提及捐款 700 萬元人民幣（約 HK$798 萬），全力支持疫情防控工作。<br />\n<br />\n高通 Qualcomm 在微博出 post 表示捐款 700 萬元人民幣（約 HK$798 萬）<br />\n品牌提到全力支持疫情防控工作<br />\n早前 Starbucks 中國、MediaTek 也在微博出 post 表示已捐款幫助採購醫療物資及支持抗疫<br />\n<br />\n相對 Starbucks 中國在微博的支持疫情防控 post，Qualcomm 中國的微博 post 就相對簡要，當中提及「Qualcomm 將向中國相關組織捐款 700 萬元人民幣，支持新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎疫情的防控工作。我們向所有受到疫情影響的人們表示衷心的慰問，向所有奮戰在疫情防控一線的工作人員致以崇高的敬意！」<br />\n<br />\n雖然有微博網民認為 Qualcomm 作為全球知名科企，沒理由捐出這麼少的金錢支持疫情防控工作，不過有反駁的網民認為在這個艱難時刻，捐款金額多少都是心意。說來科技界除了 Qualcomm 有捐款表心意外，MediaTek 亦向武漢東湖高新區政府捐贈價值 1,000 萬元人民幣（約 HK$1,140 萬）的醫療相關物資，用於新型冠狀病毒肺炎的疫情防控工作。"},{"pid":"8fd337b83d7dbe76c5fa121c0a73d24c5bf6cc64","tid":1853355,"uid":3171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:30:59.000Z","msg":"【連儂牆】元朗西鐵站看「文宣」遭多人揮棍圍毆　6青年受傷送院<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853160</a><br />\n<br />\n721再現 唔可以比佢沉"},{"pid":"63a243d63da64e40ade1fa44b6161ea798b3a2df","tid":1853355,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:44:22.000Z","msg":"貿易戰驚閪咩，大把美國公司爭住補血<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11294d8a73bcf2cda230fca10a722a3b1f279e27","tid":1853355,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:45:33.000Z","msg":"上面咁有錢捐錢唔捐物質有咩用"},{"pid":"85725b6e9f0283d9a26ddd9a29df8133e0647aa1","tid":1853355,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:15:52.000Z","msg":"捐錢比匪賊來搶自己的科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c5595b07133ec9f894d829e458c5ea31de0639","tid":1853355,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"仲捐得多過Microsoft Sony<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}